text:
Hi! This is a great app, I post some stuff on there everyone and there but mostly watch other's videos. I would recommend the app a lot more if this issues were fixed;

 Dark/light mode. I really don't care which one this app prefers, and I don't care if it stays as light mode without an option to change it to dark mode or vise versa. But what bothers me is having BOTH ON. Like for an example, I'll be watching a video right? The like button and all that stuff will be set the dark mode. then I go into the comments section and it will stay as dark mode but the text will become black so that I can't read it. Amazing right? Wrong. That's very annoying and please get rid of it

P.S: Can you guys add community posts on an IPad please? Just make it like the phone but wider. Ty!
